        <item>
            <title>FUJIFILM 最搶手即影即有出 Wide 版    「instax WIDE Evo」大玩不同攝影效果 + 影到靚先印</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/23/instax-wide-evo/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=instax-wide-evo</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/23/instax-wide-evo/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 12:00:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[instax WIDE Evo]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1288483</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Fujifilm 宣佈推出全新混合式即影即有相機「instax WIDE Evo」，Evo 上代一出即賣斷市，今代 WIDE Evo 就支援寬幅 WIDE 格式菲林，廠方稱可實現多達 10 萬種攝影效果選擇。相機預計於 2025 年 2 月 6 日發售，售價為 HKD 2,798。</p><h4></h4><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288486" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-144x144.jpeg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288487" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-1-694x462.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-1-694x462.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-1.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-3-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-3-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-3.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-3-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>「instax WIDE Evo」延續傳統菲林相機的操作理念，機身採用黑色基調搭配金屬質感，復古外觀更添奢華感。相機配備 LCD 屏幕，支援用户即時取景，並挑選心儀照片打印。相機更加入「玩味」設計，用户可手動操作菲林轉盤及列印搖桿，可以手動把印好的菲林「攪」出來，模擬傳統相機體驗，進一步提升即影即有相機的趣味性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288494" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-2.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-2-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h4></h4><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288492" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288488" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-2-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-2-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-2.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-2-144x144.jpeg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>新一代「WIDE Evo」提供 10 種菲林效果（如「品紅」和「黑白」）及 10 種鏡頭效果（如「漏光」和「色彩漸變」），並加入首次推出的「微調」功能，用户可細緻調整光線強度和色彩漸變，達到 100 級的精確調節。這種效果的組合與微調，令攝影選項多達 100,000 種，讓每張作品更具創意。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288484 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025012342716-571x580.jpg" alt="" width="571" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025012342716-571x580.jpg 571w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025012342716.jpg 886w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 571px" /></p><p>WIDE Evo 新增「菲林風格」與「廣角模式」兩大功能。「菲林風格」提供六種風格化相框設計，使照片更具藝術感；而「廣角模式」則進一步擴展畫面範圍，適合拍攝壯麗風景或熱鬧場景。</p><div class="mceTemp"></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288485 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025012342706-551x580.jpg" alt="" width="551" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025012342706-551x580.jpg 551w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025012342706.jpg 856w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 551px" /></p><p>專屬手機應用程式提供「探索動態」功能，讓用户瀏覽全球「WIDE Evo」作品，從中獲取靈感。應用程式亦支援效果複製，用户可透過藍牙將其他作品的效果複製至自己的相機，輕鬆實現個性化創作。除此之外，相機還可作為智能手機打印機，直接列印手機內的照片。配合「instax WIDE Evo」的推出，富士還同步推出專用相機保護套（HKD 400）及全新 WIDE 格式菲林「磨砂金屬感」（HKD 120），以豐富用户的攝影選擇。</p><div class="page" title="Page 7"><div class="section"><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57853248" width="98.784000" height="0.960000" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57865728" width="218.300000" height="0.959990" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57866688" width="133.700000" height="0.959990" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57867072" width="98.784000" height="0.959990" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-1.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-1-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57866880" width="218.300000" height="0.480010" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57862848" width="133.700000" height="0.480010" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57867264" width="98.784000" height="0.480010" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57867456" width="218.300000" height="0.480000" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57867648" width="133.700000" height="0.480000" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57867840" width="98.784000" height="0.480000" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57868032" width="218.300000" height="0.960010" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57802944" width="133.700000" height="0.960010" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57805056" width="98.784000" height="0.960010" /></div></div><p>資料來源：Fujifilm</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/23/instax-wide-evo/dc/">FUJIFILM 最搶手即影即有出 Wide 版    「instax WIDE Evo」大玩不同攝影效果 + 影到靚先印</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
